<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink115">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>amma vāḻi tōḻi paṉmā</l>
<l>nuṇmaṇa laṭaikarai nammō ṭāṭiya</l>
<l>taṇṇan tuṟaivaṉ maṟaii</l>
<l>yaṉṉai yaruṅkaṭi vantuniṉ ṟōṉē</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Oh friend, listen!</l>
<l>The man from the cool, pretty ghat</l>
<l>Who played with us on the shore upon which numerous, great, fine grains of sand were deposited,</l>
<l>Having come secretly [through] mother's difficult guard, stands [here].</l>
</lg>
    </div>
